雷西·怀尔斯 (Tracey Wiles) 因在<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/baldurs-gate-3">《博德之门 3》</a></em>中扮演卡拉赫和贾希拉的演员而获得奖项，在进场前摆了张合影。</p><h3><strong>说到风格……</strong> </h3><figure id="attachment_3617052" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3617052" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3617052" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Chandana-Ekanayake-and-Meghna-Jayanth-BAFTA-Games.jpg" alt="Chandana Ekanayake（左）和 Meghna Jayanth（右）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Chandana-Ekanayake-and-Meghna-Jayanth-BAFTA-Games.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Chandana-Ekanayake-and-Meghna-Jayanth-BAFTA-Games-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Chandana-Ekanayake-and-Meghna-Jayanth-BAFTA-Games-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Chandana-Ekanayake-and-Meghna-Jayanth-BAFTA-Games-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Chandana-Ekanayake-and-Meghna-Jayanth-BAFTA-Games-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Chandana-Ekanayake-and-Meghna-Jayanth-BAFTA-Games-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3617052" class="wp-caption-text"> Chandana Ekanayake（左）和 Meghna Jayanth（右）。图片来源：Shane Anthony Sinclair/BAFTA/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> Chandana Ekanayake 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/boss-level-2022-meghna-jayanth-is-switching-the-narrative-3331160">Meghna Jayanth</a>在代表<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/outerloop-games">Outerloop Games</a>的非凡角色扮演游戏<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/thirsty-suitors"><em>《Thirsty Suitors》</em></a>时盛装打扮。</p><h3><strong>红地毯上的蜘蛛侠</strong></h3><figure id="attachment_3617055" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3617055" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" 